{
  "stem": "5496.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some friends say that I'm an envy of all of them because I find joy in simple things of life.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, I don't want to sound like Pollyanna, but material things truly are not my priority.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I see sunshine, as you can see, I'm wearing yellow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They are always-- my friends think I'm synonymous with sunshine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I rejoice in it and flowers and every little bit of life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I try to be good and do kindness whenever I can.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And as my friends will attest to it, I'm always the first to come to day aid whenever they need me, and so does my family.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I try to be good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That's my primary religion, to try to be good and decent.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And no matter what your religion, I see no distinction.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the message would be summed up-- it's interesting you should ask.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in Vienna just a few weeks ago, and there is a memorial in the middle of Vienna right next to their opera, because-- Fred, of course, he saw it himself-- they took elderly Jews, and on all four, they had to scrub the street with a toothbrush.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there is, indeed, a statue depicting such a Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as-- whenever I'm in Vienna I make sure that I go there and I place some flowers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this trip, as all others, I've been there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And a group of schoolchildren happened to come with a teacher, and I asked whether they know what it is.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They'd never been there, and the teacher was obviously taking them for a reason.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in my best German, which is quite atrocious, but I managed to explain what cruelty to men does and to learn to be good and to respect each other whatever your religion.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
